import anndata as ad
import scanpy as sc
from lassoview import *

adata = ad.read_h5ad('./data/newdataset.h5ad')
# sc.pp.neighbors(adata)

#  t-SNE
sc.tl.tsne(adata)  # t-SNEt-SNE
sc.pl.tsne(adata, color='annotation', title='Original data image')  # 
del adata
for i in range(0, 10):
    # Corresponding adata can be downloaded in MetaInfo or use the code as following.
    adata = ad.read_h5ad('./data/newdataset.h5ad')
    # 
    with open(f'./data/test/{i}.txt', 'r') as f:
        # 
        first_line = f.readline().strip()  # 
        lassoed_index = eval(first_line)  #  eval 
    
    refined_index = LPARefine(selected=lassoed_index,adata=adata, function="anndata", do_correct=True)
    print(refined_index)
    
    #  'highlight' 
    adata.obs['annotation'] = list(adata.obs['annotation'])
    adata.obs['annotation'].iloc[refined_index] = "Chosen_Cell"
    adata.obs['annotation'].iloc[lassoed_index] = "Chosen_Cell"
    adata.obs['annotation'] = adata.obs['annotation'].astype("category")
    #  UMAP 'highlight'  'refined'  'other' 
    # sc.pl.umap(adata, color='highlight', title='Highlighted Refined Cells', palette=['gray', 'red'])
    sc.tl.umap(adata)  # UMAP
    sc.pl.umap(adata, color='annotation', title='UMAP of Cells',legend_loc='on data')  # 
    
    #  t-SNE
    # sc.tl.tsne(adata)  # t-SNEt-SNE
    # sc.pl.tsne(adata, color='annotation', title=f'File {i} Cell Selection Image')  # 
    del adata
